            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1633340172790-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1633340172790-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>caramelised mushrooms</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray and put in the oven to keep warm</p><p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken breast </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 7-8 min or until browned</p>",
