    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> roughly and chop your<strong> chives</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 750ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[1L]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1633340179779-x200.jpg",
