          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1633340179779-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped chives</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) to the pan with a knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Cook for 30 secs or until softened</p><p>Add your <strong>arborio rice</strong> and<strong> chopped garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the butter</p><p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until it's evaporated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1633340183866-x200.jpg",
