    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, remove the risotto from the heat and stir in the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and<strong> clotted cream</strong></p><p>Remove the <strong>caramelised mushrooms</strong> from the oven and add <strong>half</strong> to the pan (save the other half for garnish!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy chicken breast, mushroom & chive risotto</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of boiled water if your risotto is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
