      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy chicken breast, mushroom & chive risotto</strong> topped with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>caramelised</strong> <strong>mushrooms</strong></p><p>Garnish with a sprinkle of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>chives</strong> and season with a generous grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
